description:
#Repost susies_truth:
Not soooo silent protest 😁
.
.
Just to be clear.. I completely boycott wearing masks anytime at any place. My intuition just told me that I need to go home to Germany to see my mum & friends as long as it’s still possible. And I understand that, if I book a flight I agree to the companies terms & conditions, which includes wearing masks these days. I‘m totally willing to pay that price in order to hug my loved ones.
Still I’m a rebel by heart, so here‘s my compromise.
Do what you can with what you have where you’re at 😉
.
